## 2단계: FrmMain.cs — BWD 배열 추가 + InitControl_Noise 반영

### 필드 선언 추가 (기존 FWD 배열 옆에)
```csharp
private ZedGraphControl[] GraphBwd;
private System.Windows.Forms.Label[] SpecStartUpBwd;
private System.Windows.Forms.Label[] SpecOperatingBwd;
private System.Windows.Forms.Label[] ValStartUpBwd;
private System.Windows.Forms.Label[] ValOperatingBwd;
private System.Windows.Forms.Label[] DecStartUpBwd;
private System.Windows.Forms.Label[] DecOperatingBwd;
```

### Control2Arry()에 BWD 바인딩 추가
```csharp
GraphBwd = BindControlsByIndex<ZedGraphControl>(this, "Graph_BWD", 4);
SpecStartUpBwd = BindControlsByIndex<Label>(this, "Spec_StartUp_BWD", 4);
SpecOperatingBwd = BindControlsByIndex<Label>(this, "Spec_Operating_BWD", 4);
ValStartUpBwd = BindControlsByIndex<Label>(this, "Val_StartUp_BWD", 4);
ValOperatingBwd = BindControlsByIndex<Label>(this, "Val_Operating_BWD", 4);
DecStartUpBwd = BindControlsByIndex<Label>(this, "Dec_StartUp_BWD", 4);
DecOperatingBwd = BindControlsByIndex<Label>(this, "Dec_Operating_BWD", 4);
```

### InitControl_Noise() 수정
기존 FWD 초기화 코드 아래에 BWD 초기화 추가:
```csharp
// BWD 그래프 초기화
ClassZedGraph.InitGraph(GraphBwd[0], "Motor#1 BWD NOISE", "dB", 10, 90, curveColor: Color.DarkBlue, lineWidth: 2.5f);
ClassZedGraph.InitGraph(GraphBwd[1], "Motor#1 BWD CURRENT", "A", 0, 1, curveColor: Color.DarkBlue, lineWidth: 2.5f);
ClassZedGraph.InitGraph(GraphBwd[2], "Motor#2 BWD NOISE", "dB", 10, 90, curveColor: Color.DarkBlue, lineWidth: 2.5f);
ClassZedGraph.InitGraph(GraphBwd[3], "Motor#2 BWD CURRENT", "A", 0, 1, curveColor: Color.DarkBlue, lineWidth: 2.5f);

// BWD 라벨 초기화
for (int i = 0; i < 4; i++)
{
    SpecStartUpBwd[i].Text = "";
    SpecOperatingBwd[i].Text = "";
    ValStartUpBwd[i].Text = "";
    ValOperatingBwd[i].Text = "";
    DecStartUpBwd[i].Text = "";
    DecOperatingBwd[i].Text = "";
    DecStartUpBwd[i].BackColor = bgDec;
    DecOperatingBwd[i].BackColor = bgDec;
}
```

## 주의사항
- FrmMain.cs를 먼저 읽어서 현재 코드 구조 확인 후 수정
- 기존 FWD 로직(NoiseCurrentTest 호출, ShowBasic_Noise 등)은 건드리지 않음
- BWD 동작 로직은 추가하지 않음 (InitControl_Noise 초기화만)
- 빌드 확인 필수

